##
## half_hour	-  30 minutes
## one_hour	-   1 hour
## three_hour   -   3 hours
## six_hour     -   6 hours
## half_day	-  12 hours
## one_day	-  24 hours
## two_day	-  48 hours
## five_day	- 120 hours
